sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client Input
    participant Proxy as PlayerNetworkProxy
    participant Server as ServerAuthority Module
    participant Logic as LogicLayer
    participant NetState as NetworkVariable / NetworkList
    participant Event as EventCenter
    participant View as UI / RenderLayer

    Client->>Proxy: Fire / CastSkill / Interact
    Proxy->>Server: ServerRpc request
    Server->>Server: Validate sender and ownership
    Server->>Logic: Execute authoritative logic
    Logic-->>Server: Result
    Server->>NetState: Update replicated state
    Server->>Event: Trigger authoritative event
    NetState-->>Client: Replicate state
    Event->>View: Refresh HUD / VFX / DamageText

